            "description": "World's Best News is an awareness campaign and news information service. It is part of a European network which aims to draw attention to positive global developments and progress in developing countries. The world is making huge progress, but this doesn't receive much attention in the mainstream news. World's Best News thinks it is time for a new balance in the coverage of global trends. \n\nWorld's Best News tries to convince mainstream media to publish or broadcast news on progress and successes and not only about problems and disasters. Besides that, Worlds Best News tries to convince governments, NGOs and businesses to show that their efforts to solve problems have beared fruit. There is much progress everywhere - but we rarely hear about it. \n",
